BarChart

Load ggplot

Marital1 <- read.table(
    header=TRUE, text='Year        Marital Percent
    1   `1960`       Married      .71
    2  `2010`       Married      .52
    3  `1960` Single      .15
    4   `2010` Single      .28
    5   `1960`     Divorced       .05
    6  `2010`     Divorced       .14
    7   `1960`       Widowed      .09
    8  `2010`       Widowed     .06')
ggplot(Marital1, xlab = "marital Status", aes(reorder(factor(Marital),-Percent), Percent, fill = Year)) + 
    geom_bar(stat="identity", position = "dodge") + 
    scale_fill_brewer(palette = "Set2")
